    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 assessment table. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts NIH within 6.2% of FDA benchmark data across the full COU operating envelope. Dimensional tolerance sensitivity sweep confirms RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion satisfied for all 48 tolerance combinations. Model credibility is sufficient to support the Class II CPB device submission decision.",
